---
title: Orange-Cherry Glazed Pork Steak with Chive Mash & Macadamia Veggies
description: The table has been laid, there’s wrapping on the floor and bellies are rumbling in anticipation for this fruitful dinner
spread. A festive orange and cherry glaze has been whipped up to bring a smile to this pork steak. The luxurious
addition of crushed macadamias to the veggies is the cherry on top.

 *This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
